  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To Save Severe Malnourished Children in Bihar.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nidan is running a Nutritional Rehabilitation Centre in Bihar. The project helps severe and acute malnourished (SAM) children in the age group of 6 months to 60 months. It&apos;s a facility-based care which provides nutritious food &amp; medication to children &amp; mothers. They are discharged only after complete recovery. Mothers are trained on feed preparation, basic healthcare, hygiene and nutrition. So far Nidan has saved 1189 SAM children and wants to save more with your generous support.</narrative>
  </description>
